<dl id="n16013h"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n16" href="#n16013h">N16 (VI.D.1)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n16all.htm#n16013h"> 13(h)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <font face="wake">H</font> opium</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"> I am much less inclined to put my trust in the advance of pharmacology than Mr Haldane and Mr Russell! Hitherto new drugs have only meant new vices, sometimes (like <mark>cocaine</mark>) of so fascinating a character as to distract the whole police force from their proper function of repressing crime. <small> F.C.S. Schiller, <a name="TANT" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#TANT"><cite title="source">Tantalus</cite></a> (1924) 75</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c02135h" href="c02all.htm#c02135h">VI.C.02:135(h)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
